Class DestinationCard

java.lang.Object
  Card
      DestinationCard

public class DestinationCard
extends Card

This DestinationCard class inherits from the Card class. This class will store the cities and values on a destination card. It will be able to separate a large String and split it into two cities and the value on that card.

Version:
April 10, 2013
Author:
Chan Tran, Dan Egan, Damian Crisafulli, Andrew Reynolds, Matt Brancato
